KITCHEN HAS 2 WALL OVENS, BUILT-IN PANTRY, QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, AND MORE. SS APPLIANCE PACKAGE IS KITCHEN AID. 4TH BEDROOM HAS PRIVACY POCKET DOOR AND FULL BATH THAT ALSO ACTS AS THE CABANA BATH. BREATHTAKING LARGE BACKYARD WITH POOL AND LOTS OF PRIVACY ALONG WITH OVERSIZED COVERED PATIO. CAMERA SYSTEM FOR PREMITER OF HOME STAYS WITH THE HOME.  THIS IS A MUST SEE AND PRICED RIGHT.
